title: hnn-core Parameter Schema
description: This is the json-schema for validating hnn-core param dictionaries. All input and trial-specific params must be explicitly defined. Evoked input params that go undefined will remain non-existent in the resulting simulation. Cell and network parameters will be assigned default values for missing key/value pairs consistent with the values in the 'default.json' param file.
